      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "\"I think if you don't have clarity about why you're going in, you have no way of knowing how the hell to get out.\" - @GovernorShapiro @RealTimers\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2033982925814043026",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-17T19:04:53+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Jerry O'Connell this week at @ClubRandom_!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2033948547146785046",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-17T16:48:17+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Hollywood isn't a secret cabal of racists; it's a secret cabal of people terrified of looking like racists. #OscarsSoWrong\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2032659311265198405",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T03:25:19+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "It's Friday the 13th! I'm not superstitious, but if you're in Tehran, don't walk under a leader.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2032659152154263797",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T03:24:41+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Calling all social justice warriors.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2031766395445453192",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T16:17:11+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Sam Harris is back this week at @ClubRandom_!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2031044341586854326",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-09T16:28:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "bill-maher",
      "voiceName": "Bill Maher",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Can we all go back and be nicer for a change?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/billmaher/status/2030136273202286634",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-07T04:19:40+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
